name: Strategic Reserves (V)
Lore: 'The Empire is able to quickly relocate its manpower, deploying its troops as efficiently as possible.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Your clones and Coruscant guards are destiny +1 when drawn for weapon or battle destiny. Once per turn, may cancel a Force drain by placing here from hand a clone or Coruscant guard. Characters may deploy from here as if from hand.',
